    Yes, but only hatchery steelhead. Wild steelhead must be released in most rivers — check current regulations.
</p>
<p>
    <strong>4. What is the legal fishing time in winter?</strong><br>
    Generally, fishing is allowed one hour before sunrise to one hour after sunset, but verify with ODFW guidelines.
</p>
<p>
    <strong>5. Are there kid-friendly spots to try steelhead fishing?</strong><br>
